A highly trained dog, Sully can perform a number of commands, including opening doors and fetching items such as the phone when it rings.He will now work as a service dog, assisting with therapy for wounded soldiers.Sully has his own Instagram account; here he is shown "assisting with voting" as Mr Bush cast his ballot in last month's US presidential mid-term election.
    
        
